1
00:00:06,540 --> 00:00:10,940
[Bound by Sin]

2
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:13,980
[Episode 7]

3
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:25,480
Miss Zhou refuses to leave.

4
00:00:26,120 --> 00:00:27,160
She insists on seeing you.

5
00:00:27,710 --> 00:00:28,350
Got it.

6
00:00:41,920 --> 00:00:42,470
Have a seat.

7
00:00:51,070 --> 00:00:52,000
Hello, Miss Jiang.

8
00:00:52,790 --> 00:00:53,640
I'm Zhou Xiaoqing.

9
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:55,920
Sorry to intrude today.

10
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,240
It's fine.

11
00:00:59,150 --> 00:00:59,840
Miss Zhou,

12
00:01:00,030 --> 00:01:01,150
how can I help you?

13
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:05,760
Miss Jiang,

14
00:01:06,790 --> 00:01:08,430
I know you and Dongyang are engaged,

15
00:01:09,350 --> 00:01:10,710
but he doesn't love you.

16
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,510
He never has.

17
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,040
If he did,

18
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:16,150
he wouldn't have been with me for so long.

19
00:01:17,150 --> 00:01:17,870
Miss Jiang,

20
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:19,920
I just don't get it.

21
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,430
Why would someone as wealthy as you

22
00:01:22,590 --> 00:01:23,790
choose to be

23
00:01:23,790 --> 00:01:25,480
with a man who doesn't love you?

24
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,280
Miss Jiang,

25
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,760
please, let him be with me.

26
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:32,760
Miss Zhou,

27
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:33,680
please get up.

28
00:01:43,070 --> 00:01:43,790
Miss Zhou,

29
00:01:44,430 --> 00:01:46,200
what's your definition of wealth?

30
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:53,680
Money is money only within a certain range.

31
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,640
Miss Jiang,

32
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,640
I don't understand what you mean.

33
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:01,920
Once it goes beyond that range,

34
00:02:02,590 --> 00:02:03,950
it's no longer just money.

35
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,040
It's a person's entire life at stake.

36
00:02:06,510 --> 00:02:08,520
No one would give up their own life willingly.

37
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,120
I won't,

38
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,150
and Shen Dongyang certainly won't either.

39
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,630
Miss Zhou,

40
00:02:16,030 --> 00:02:16,710
please leave.

41
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,080
I always do everything he says.

42
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,080
I wear whatever he tells me to wear

43
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,470
and speak the way he likes.

44
00:02:35,870 --> 00:02:37,590
Am I not doing a good job of imitating her?

45
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,080
Miss Zhou,

46
00:02:44,870 --> 00:02:46,360
what did you mean by that?

47
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:48,080
Who are you imitating?

48
00:02:50,870 --> 00:02:51,870
I can't break up with him.

49
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,310
He cares about me.

50
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:56,840
I must head back now and behave myself.

51
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:57,430
Ke Rui,

52
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,470
see Miss Zhou out.

53
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,000
Let's go, Miss Zhou.

54
00:03:06,020 --> 00:03:08,620
♪When can I♪

55
00:03:08,940 --> 00:03:11,700
♪Stop panicking...♪

56
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:16,630
What rouge and perfume

57
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:17,870
has Miss Jiang been using lately?

58
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:19,960
I can't tell you.

59
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:21,470
Miss Zhou,

60
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,240
since you've chosen to be a mistress,

61
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,630
learn not to overstep your boundaries.

62
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:26,910
Take care.

63
00:03:28,060 --> 00:03:33,340
♪Why am I still greedy?♪

64
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:34,360
Miss,

65
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:35,360
please.

66
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:39,380
♪When I take off the evening dress naked♪

67
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:43,300
♪But my eyes still look dull...♪

68
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:45,680
Up until now,

69
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,430
Zhou Xiaoqing still doesn't understand

70
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,590
what she did wrong

71
00:03:49,630 --> 00:03:51,710
or why Shen Dongyang suddenly turned on her.

72
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,080
That morning,

73
00:03:54,590 --> 00:03:56,870
she and Shen Dongyang had breakfast together for the first time in ages,

74
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:59,560
so sweet it felt like they were just any ordinary couple.

75
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:05,820
♪I might as well forget my wandering days...♪

76
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:06,910
Dongyang,

77
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:10,560
how often do you see your fiancée in a year?

78
00:04:12,430 --> 00:04:13,360
Not as much as I see you.

79
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:17,390
What does she look like?

80
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:19,070
Is she as pretty as me?

81
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,510
Answer me.

82
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,800
What does she look like?

83
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,040
Is she as pretty as me?

84
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,270
Is she ugly?

85
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,800
Is that why she never shows her face?

86
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:37,500
♪When I take off the evening dress naked♪

87
00:04:37,740 --> 00:04:41,460
♪But my eyes still look dull...♪

88
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,190
Why aren't you saying anything?

89
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,430
Is she cheating on you?

90
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,390
Did you have me dress up like her

91
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,310
because she won't let you touch her?

92
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,630
Zhou Xiaoqing,

93
00:04:56,070 --> 00:04:57,830
stop being such a lunatic.

94
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,430
Shen Dongyang, stop right there!

95
00:05:02,190 --> 00:05:03,800
If you walk out that door today,

96
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,480
don't ever come back to me.

97
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:08,040
There are plenty of rich, powerful men chasing after me,

98
00:05:09,310 --> 00:05:10,720
and none of them are as twisted as you!

99
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:14,140
♪I might as well be frank♪

100
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:18,380
♪On a peaceful evening...♪

101
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,360
Shen Dongyang!

102
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,040
That was just angry talk.

103
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,270
I just wanted to hear him say,

104
00:05:27,750 --> 00:05:28,750
"You're beautiful."

105
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:41,920
What is it?

106
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:45,630
Are you going to lecture me again, Mr. Fu?

107
00:05:47,630 --> 00:05:48,720
So, you're marrying

108
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,510
Shen Dongyang no matter what, right?

109
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,870
Is there something wrong with that?

110
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:54,310
Even if he's been hurting you,

111
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,070
fooling around with women,

112
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,070
causing scandals,

113
00:05:58,310 --> 00:05:59,430
and getting another woman

114
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:00,600
to dress up like you?

115
00:06:01,630 --> 00:06:02,390
Don't you find that...?

116
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,270
What?

117
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:08,950
Disgusting?

118
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:14,720
Mr. Fu, you really are

119
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:16,630
quite naive.

120
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,040
The purer someone is,

121
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,950
the more it makes people want

122
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,560
to destroy them.

123
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,270
Do you like them?

124
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,270
Do you know what I do, looking at these photos,

125
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:52,430
when I stay late at the office?

126
00:07:06,220 --> 00:07:09,100
♪You were a storm, scattering...♪

127
00:07:09,310 --> 00:07:09,950
You...

128
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,560
How could you...?

129
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:12,830
Why not?

130
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:17,140
♪The wreckage, what do you want me to do with it?♪

131
00:07:17,300 --> 00:07:21,780
♪I pick it up, then throw it back into my memories♪

132
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:25,060
♪I hide in this fragile room♪

133
00:07:25,220 --> 00:07:29,020
♪Shedding tears, blaming you for your sweet words♪

134
00:07:29,260 --> 00:07:32,500
♪What gave you the strength to move on from us?♪

135
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:37,460
♪Leaving silently without a trace♪

136
00:07:38,300 --> 00:07:41,100
♪You were a ruthless storm♪

137
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:45,620
♪Drowning my love, offering no respite♪

138
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:49,140
♪I'm in my thin clothes, curled up♪

139
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:53,660
♪In the silence you left me, without a word♪

140
00:07:54,260 --> 00:07:57,060
♪How am I supposed to face this endgame♪

141
00:07:57,300 --> 00:08:01,460
♪Without you by my side?♪

142
00:08:02,260 --> 00:08:03,900
♪Your warmth and sweetness♪

143
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:06,020
♪Are etched in my mind♪

144
00:08:06,260 --> 00:08:09,740
♪How am I supposed to forget?♪

145
00:08:18,980 --> 00:08:21,020
[Jiang's Trading Company]

146
00:08:25,380 --> 00:08:28,980
[Jiang Yingxian's third eldest granduncle]

147
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,670
Boss.

148
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:42,720
Yingxian.

149
00:08:42,790 --> 00:08:43,440
Granduncle.

150
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:47,200
Let me get down on my knees first.

151
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:48,000
Granduncle!

152
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,480
Let's talk over there.

153
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:55,240
Alright.

154
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:03,550
Have a seat.

155
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,240
Be careful.

156
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,080
Isn't this all

157
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:16,080
such a headache?

158
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:17,240
I really don't know...

159
00:09:53,460 --> 00:09:56,980
[Jiang's Trading Company]

160
00:10:12,510 --> 00:10:14,750
The more time I spend with Jiang Yingxian,

161
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:17,670
the more I find myself naturally respecting her,

162
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:19,030
admiring her,

163
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,600
and feeling for her.

164
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:26,320
♪Love is not our destiny♪

165
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:30,800
♪I asked the wind when you'd be back...♪

166
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,630
She's nothing like the rich young ladies

167
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:35,390
I've known.

168
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:39,030
Her time and energy

169
00:10:39,870 --> 00:10:41,840
[Jiang's Trading Company]
are all devoted to the Jiang family.

170
00:10:49,170 --> 00:10:51,060
[Jiang's Trading Company]

171
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,600
Ke Rui told me you went out,

172
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:13,480
but I knew I'd find you here.

173
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:14,480
As expected,

174
00:11:14,870 --> 00:11:16,440
we are in tune with each other.

175
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:18,270
You seem eager to see me.

176
00:11:18,510 --> 00:11:19,390
Let's talk upstairs.

177
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,630
I came to apologize,

178
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,390
and I hope you can

179
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,480
spare some time to have dinner with me.

180
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:28,200
It would be my honor.

181
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:32,270
In that case, Mr. Fu,

182
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:35,080
please let me take over from here.

183
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,750
Let us, as an engaged couple,

184
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,910
have some time alone.

185
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:45,440
Mr. Fu, you can leave early today.

186
00:12:10,700 --> 00:12:13,140
[Jiang's Trading Company]

187
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:31,080
I only ordered this today.

188
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,750
You don't mind, do you?

189
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:34,600
Of course not.

190
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,630
Zhou Xiaoqing

191
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:53,150
came to see you a few days ago, right?

192
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,200
Yes.

193
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,440
Is Shen Dongyang mad?

194
00:12:59,270 --> 00:13:00,510
Is he unhappy with how I reacted?

195
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:01,840
Why?

196
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:04,000
This is your personal matter.

197
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:05,240
I shouldn't interfere,

198
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:06,510
but I do think

199
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:09,240
you could've handled it better.

200
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:11,320
Well...

201
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:14,150
You haven't changed at all, Jiang Yingxian.

202
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,910
But she told me everything

203
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,440
you two talked about.

204
00:13:20,030 --> 00:13:20,670
Oh, did she?

205
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:22,480
I see.

206
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,600
As his fiancée,

207
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,720
when his mistress showed up at my door,

208
00:13:27,150 --> 00:13:28,120
I was supposed to be angry,

209
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:29,360
upset,

210
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:32,480
or at least throw out a few sarcastic remarks,

211
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:35,270
even though that would only annoy him.

212
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:36,630
The point is,

213
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,720
in his eyes, there can only be people who are rejected by him,

214
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,480
not the other way around.

215
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,630
Did you tell her

216
00:13:49,510 --> 00:13:51,320
your life is on the line because of me?

217
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:52,960
Yes.

218
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,120
Isn't that true?

219
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:56,670
Good.

220
00:13:57,150 --> 00:13:58,080
Straightforward as always.

221
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:01,510
It suits our relationship, which is based on mutual benefits.

222
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:05,480
There are ways to handle a relationship built on interests,

223
00:14:06,870 --> 00:14:10,200
and there are ways to handle one based on love.

224
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,240
Yingxian,

225
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:17,000
how do you want to handle ours?

226
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:20,440
If I can't fall in love with Shen Dongyang,

227
00:14:21,510 --> 00:14:23,630
then I'll have no choice but to stick to the former.

228
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:27,360
I hope my self-punishment will be enough

229
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,030
to make him drop the topic.

230
00:14:31,620 --> 00:14:34,260
♪I don't have the courage to face the scars of the past♪

231
00:14:34,420 --> 00:14:36,500
♪After all this time, I'm still not over her♪

232
00:14:36,660 --> 00:14:37,940
♪I ask myself, am I at peace?♪

233
00:14:38,020 --> 00:14:40,100
♪Can I let go? Do I regret it?♪

234
00:14:40,220 --> 00:14:42,900
♪But time can never turn back♪

235
00:14:43,060 --> 00:14:47,260
♪I can only carry these memories and meet her in my dreams♪

236
00:15:00,340 --> 00:15:02,580
♪Imagination and reality are always at odds♪

237
00:15:03,140 --> 00:15:05,380
♪Plans can never keep up with changes♪

238
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:07,660
♪We're caught between love and what's right♪

239
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:10,580
♪There's nothing we can do about it♪

240
00:15:11,700 --> 00:15:14,500
♪We tell the ones we love that we've never loved them♪

241
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:17,060
♪We act clueless in front of those we don't love♪

242
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:18,780
♪Listening to those who don't love us♪

243
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:21,620
♪Saying how much they love us with sweet words♪

244
00:15:22,180 --> 00:15:23,580
♪I ask myself, is the love still there?♪

245
00:15:23,780 --> 00:15:25,740
♪Have I moved on? Should I let go?♪

246
00:15:25,940 --> 00:15:28,420
♪Is she still in my heart?♪

