00:15:51,620 --> 00:15:54,260
♪I don't have the courage to face the scars of the past♪

254
00:15:54,420 --> 00:15:56,500
♪After all this time, I'm still not over her♪

255
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:04,080
Enough, Jiang Yingxian.

256
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:07,240
Stop drinking.

257
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:11,550
Have you had your fill, Mr. Shen?

258
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,670
I brought this from Haicheng.

259
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,390
You haven't eaten anything today.

260
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:22,360
Take it home. Have it as a late-night snack.

261
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:30,790
You could've smoothed things over with a few sweet words,

262
00:16:32,150 --> 00:16:33,080
but no,

263
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:35,390
you chose to drink

264
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,550
and throw soft jabs at me.

265
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:40,030
What a troublesome personality.

266
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:42,750
Thank you for the gift.

267
00:16:44,150 --> 00:16:45,240
Let me walk you home.

268
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:47,630
It's okay.

269
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:50,360
Ke Rui will take me back.

270
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:11,640
Zhou Xiaoqing

271
00:17:13,240 --> 00:17:15,550
really doesn't deserve any sympathy.

272
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:18,400
The moment she saw him, she sold me out completely.

273
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:20,920
Her tears are genuine,

274
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:22,480
but her manipulations are real too.

275
00:17:26,270 --> 00:17:27,960
Shen Dongyang and I are no different.

276
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,790
We look decent on the outside,

277
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:33,640
but inside, we're both falling apart.

278
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:38,000
I'm worse than Shen Dongyang,

